{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act33side", "eventName": "巴別塔", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BB-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "激變烽煙", "storyInfo": "內戰期間，為了巴別塔的理想而戰的特蕾西婭支持者在戰爭中大放異彩，戰爭的天平開始向巴別塔傾斜。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_battlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "1092年冬"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，邊境戰區"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_imprisonment_intro", "key": "$m_bat_imprisonment_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_animalrun", "channel": "1", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些發瘋的瘤獸……是在遷徙？該死，不光前哨部隊被衝散了，那些沒來得及躲開的人，都……", "name": "受傷的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那些完全沒有交流卻行動一致的巴別塔士兵……之前的情報裡可沒提過這些！", "name": "受傷的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是我們該操心的問題。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我的職級最高，通知活著的人馬上歸隊收攏。這批物資很重要，沒了這些，我們這個冬天不會好過。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是，長官。我們明明提前了這次行動，但還是出了問題，是不是那邊的內應——", "name": "沉著的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "內應的情報沒問題。是負責協助運送物資的傭兵坐地起價耽誤了時間，人我已經處理了。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我討厭傭兵。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#7$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多巧合……", "name": "受傷的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巧合每次都湊在一起就不是巧合了，這段時間我們莫名其妙吃的虧已經不少了。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "集中精神，巴別塔的人一定還在——", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，救——", "name": "受傷的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_animalrun", "channel": "1", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrow"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 13.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一道白芒貫穿了士兵的頭顱，在瘤獸急促的蹄聲中，他們甚至找不到攻擊的來源。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“這是第一次警告。留下物資離開，我們不會對你們動手。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清冷嘶啞的聲音在厄爾蘇拉的腦海中響起，毫無預兆。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他……死了。*薩卡茲粗口*，我們得撤退，長官！你聽到那個聲音了嗎？", "name": "沉著的士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……他們在虛張聲勢。跟緊我的位置隱蔽前進！", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人不許脫隊單獨行動！想活著就跟著大部隊一起行動！這批物資必須要送回！", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#6$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於前哨部隊，他們只能自求多福了。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們開始撤退了，果然想要直接拿下這批物資還是有困難。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“不必冒進，按博士的安排執行即可。議長說過，最高優先級的任務是保證傷亡最小化。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我心中有數，Mantra女士。", "name": "Scout"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mantra女士雙唇緊閉，但Scout的腦海中卻清晰地迴盪著她說話的聲音。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許在巴別塔隱秘行動小隊中，她是最完美的協調員。但Scout可以肯定，在敵人的心中，她會成為蠶食理智的陰影。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敵方前哨部隊已經被獸群成功切割，逃進了那片樹林。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敵人的行動是臨時起意，想必是意識到我們破解了他們的通訊暗號。但圍剿計劃還是成功了，滴水不漏。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剩下的就交給阿斯卡綸了。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸不會失敗。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也不會。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，說的也是。休息會吧，Mantra女士，您“說話”的負擔太重了。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之後的計劃不用擔心，我們有博士在。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "0,-100", "posto": "0,0"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "power": 5.0, "times": 30.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽的，誰在指揮作戰……又是惡靈？他究竟是哪個指揮官？哪個王庭的崽種？", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他能如此對我們，總有一天也能如此對你們！給這種人賣命有什麼好處！", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會活著走出這裡——", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傭兵聽到了不遠處黑暗中的呼吸，手中的刀毫無猶豫地揮斬出去。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我找到你了！", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2", "duration": 0.4, "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "240,0"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hammer", "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶……", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，你也受了這麼重的傷，你真有把握活著宰了我？", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滾開，否則我拼了命也要宰了你！", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不能拿走馬塞爾的遺物。他得回家。", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家？咳咳，咳——", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的家在……卡茲戴爾！你們——背叛了卡茲戴爾……", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metallicclick", "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傭兵的刀不斷向奧達揮去，但他只是竭力舉起自己的大錘抵擋。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傭兵的動作越來越慢，氣息也越來越弱。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "power": 5.0, "times": 30.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巴別塔……都是傻……子……", "name": "瀕死的雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……背叛了卡茲戴爾的，難道不是軍事委員會嗎？", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放鬆，他已經死了。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以後下手要果斷些，這樣受傷會更少，奧達。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這支隊伍全死了……他們應該有更榮譽的死法，而不是在恐懼的折磨裡——", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要對敵人心軟，至少現在不要。帶上馬塞爾，我們的任務已經結束了。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……還記得他的名字？", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會記著巴別塔的每一個人。活著的，死去的，有名字的，沒有名字的。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來可以救下他……我只是很難做到……無所顧忌地向同族下手。", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕是為了替馬塞爾報仇？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#4$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#4$2"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的父親死在當年的城內亂局對吧……你想過替他報仇嗎？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧達深深吸了一口氣。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我恨殺死他的人，但復仇不能改變任何事。", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$2"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很經典的論調，正義，合理，富有人文情懷。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那如果你的仇人是個滿手鮮血、冷酷無情的劊子手呢？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會說，自己是因為正義和信念殺死的對方，而不帶仇恨色彩嗎？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我不確定。", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$2"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸小姐，你會為殺死一位威脅巴別塔的傭兵而後悔嗎？", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$2"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那我也不會後悔。", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#2$2"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕我不得不……", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#9$2"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4131_odda_1#8$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，阿斯卡綸小姐！我又不知不覺說了些奇怪的話，我沒那麼重要——", "name": "奧達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4131_odda_1#8$2"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，巴別塔的每個人對殿下都很重要。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該回去了。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lock_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，巴別塔羅德島本艦"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來幹什麼？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過無數次，背叛殿下，是我自己的決定。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和軍事委員會無關，我也不是軍事委員會安排的內應。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍法處置，給個痛快吧。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我沒打算來拷問你。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶了壺酒。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不需要。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的？這可是維多利亞的果酒，不是劣質私釀。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你到底來幹嘛的？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敘敘舊。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們無話可說。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Scout沒告訴我全貌，問阿斯卡綸也不會說。她知道我們認識。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我猜，你想殺博士的原因無非幾種。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，那你猜猜看。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是個輸不起的薩卡茲，所以你只是恨博士是個外族人。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰都希望巴別塔和軍事委員會有朝一日能和平相處，你覺得凱爾希醫生和博士沒有彌合這個裂縫，而是撕開了傷口。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道還不滾？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是外族人。不僅如此，我到今天還在為薩卡茲而戰。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "酒。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_decap", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍帽？", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰讓你不多帶個杯子，監獄裡難道有酒杯嗎？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咕——哈。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你原本隊伍裡的其他人呢？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我數數，一個長槍手，一個術師，你這個拿盾的，還有個醫療兵，和一個狙擊手？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "骷髏槍，白煙，灰陽，斯特羅斯，核桃，孔小姐，小草藥。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來那個弓箭手叫小草藥。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他死了，別記仇了。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是好戰士。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果未來我手下也有年輕人，我會把他們培養成那樣的戰士。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無私，坦誠，勇猛，謹慎地選擇信念，義無反顧地奉獻自己。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵。多愁善感。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲就這麼痛恨巴別塔的外族人嗎？", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像你這種願意為特蕾西婭殿下賣命的蠢貨，很難理解那種心情。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許巴別塔確實在改變一些事，但沒有意義。不夠普遍，不夠快。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但殿下本可以不用被絆住手腳，浪費時間。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士幫了特蕾西婭議長很多。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……作為什麼？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "研究者？還是戰爭指揮官？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都有。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕他葬送那麼多薩卡茲？這種人越多，戰爭越久。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下很偉大，她一直在解決問題，解決了幾代人的衣食住行，現在又開始攻克礦石病。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可現狀呢？我們現在在和軍事委員會打仗。在和自己人打仗。這和殿下的理想根本不一樣。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，我差點忘了。你是個“雇傭兵”，但不是“薩卡茲雇傭兵”。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……說得對。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來只是陪著大家來到巴別塔。來蹚這渾水，只是因為隊伍裡的薩卡茲居多罷了。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，白煙也死了。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幹嘛特地說起她？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為你們有戲的。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人都死了。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在特蕾西婭議長的面前。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……媽的。該死。你這麼說，我都有點羡慕她了。什麼情況？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場伏擊，我和她活到最後，她的腿被法術陷阱炸斷，我拖著她在泥地裡走。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，我們遇到了特蕾西婭議長。準確地說，先遇到了博士。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個惡靈……啐，他還會親自上戰場？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來你也許不信，遠遠望過去的時候，我還以為博士是拉特蘭的修士。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為他在黑色兜帽下祈禱。和發著亮的議長一起。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使沒有跪拜，沒有儀式，即使他只是平靜地與特蕾西婭議長看著遠方。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你嘴裡的惡靈，Dr.{@nickname}，並不是一個無情的厲鬼。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在被撕扯，在孤獨中徘徊，但他依舊選擇……為巴別塔帶來勝利。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搞了半天，你是來勸我的？就憑幾張感情牌？！", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滾，拿走你的酒，你把我當什麼——", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，你不會這麼幼稚，不至於這麼看不起我。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做出決定了？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死罪難逃吧。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，博士和特蕾西婭議長都還在猶豫，但是凱爾希醫生和大部分參與行動的戰士都不想放過你。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為你的背叛，我們間接損失了幾十位戰士，兄弟。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一次，我同意凱爾希醫生的判斷。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嘖。再給我倒一杯。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛把最後那點打翻了。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來動手？", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來。沒必要讓Scout糾結，他看著狠，心裡軟。我也不想把你交給其他人。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好兄弟，我廢話這麼幾句，只是想告訴你，也許你前些日子做了一件蠢事……", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但巴別塔會記住你的名字。我們會帶著你的警示和呵斥，繼續戰鬥下去。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵。記得早點挑幾個接班人培養起來，我看你這麼好心腸，死得也早。", "name": "薩卡茲謀反者"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是啊。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，在你們薩卡茲能平穩生活在大地上的那個日子到來的時候，我們再見吧。", "name": "Ace"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_broadswordblood"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g5_furnaceplatform", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_054"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "處決了一批叛徒，以及間諜。王庭的間諜。他們氏族內部的麻煩還真不少。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦了。那支進入戰區的隊伍呢？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斥候去查了。他們襲擊了巴別塔的據點之後，封鎖了離開山脈的交通要道。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍沒有下過命令，是某個王庭的親信……不，會是敘拉古家族的陰謀嗎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概不是，根據目前的目擊情報，巫術沒有明顯的血統特徵，通訊也沒有像樣的密碼，是支雜牌軍。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……多嘴一句，長官，雖然這支隊伍不可控，但他們現在把巴別塔堵在了天災裡。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這對我們來說不是好事嗎？", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……其他指揮官和雇傭兵領袖怎麼看？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然選擇隔岸觀火。敵人要不選擇投降，要不被天災和暴徒抹殺。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，別想太多。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您下令撤出山谷，給他們留了退路，已經仁至義盡了。我很欽佩。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定我的家人也在那場天災之下呢。我都沒糾結。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你不在乎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盡量不去在乎。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rhodescom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾地區，巴別塔羅德島本艦"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來晚了。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那？", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1310_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必再從頭複述了，Ace是被臨時召集的，跟著Mantra行動就行。", "name": "Pith"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1310_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續吧，時不我待。", "name": "Pith"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1310_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情況緊急？", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（點頭示意）", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那繼續。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在天災範圍內的巴別塔成員共有兩千五百餘人。醫療人員，感染者平民，俘虜和雇傭兵傷患居多。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災的規模也比天災信使預計的更大。目前預計影響五座哨所，三條戰略要道，以及一座廢棄城鎮改建的臨時醫療據點。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們本已快撤退到天災邊界，但有雇傭兵切斷了撤退路線。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把醫療人員、傷患和平民都關在天災下面等死？", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德現在這麼瘋狂？", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不像他幹的，軍事委員會的三小股兵力已經撤離了森林，甚至刻意留了一條峽谷作為人道走廊。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1310_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……峭壁上全是軍事委員會的術師。一旦發現有武裝力量，就直接撲滅在峽谷深處。", "name": "Pith"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1310_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，軍事委員會的行蹤和目的都沒有打算遮掩，都在預計之內。", "name": "Pith"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1310_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這些突然出現，襲擊據點的雇傭兵，他們直接炸毀了交通要道和橋樑，還用源石炸藥污染了山脈裡的數處水源，毫無目的性。", "name": "Pith"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1310_1#1$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雇主是誰？", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在查。但根據為數不多的情報推測，他們很可能……無主。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出於某種純粹的報復，或是被特雷西斯拋棄後的掙扎，以及其他國家的煽動，都有可能。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無所謂。他們的領袖，我去問，我去殺。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失去領袖，沒有目標的雇傭兵就是烏合之眾。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們救人，我們在據點會合。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他們就交給你了。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後轉達一句話，殿下說了，這次行動並不是“戰役”的一部分。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們甚至該鬆口氣。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在逐漸膠著的戰場上，對抗的雙方又有了一次齊心協力的機會，且只為了一個目的……", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1300_1#1$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1300_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從天災下，拯救生命。", "name": "Mantra"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1300_1#2$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}